## BEM Methodology

Use Block-Element-Modifier naming convention for all classes.

### Structure
- **Block**: Standalone component (`.card`)
- **Element**: Part of a block (`.card__title`)
- **Modifier**: Variant of block/element (`.card--featured`, `.card__title--large`)

### Naming Pattern
```
.block {}
.block__element {}
.block--modifier {}
.block__element--modifier {}
```

### Examples

```css
/* ❌ BAD */
.card-title {}
.cardTitle {}
.card .title {}
.featured-card {}

/* ✅ GOOD - Block */
.card {
  padding: 2rem;
  background: white;
  border-radius: 0.8rem;
}

/* ✅ GOOD - Element */
.card__title {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.card__description {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  color: #666;
}

.card__footer {
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
  padding-top: 1.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid #eee;
}

/* ✅ GOOD - Modifier */
.card--featured {
  border: 2px solid gold;
}

.card__title--large {
  font-size: 2.4rem;
}
```

