## No Horizontal Scrolling

Prevent horizontal overflow on all pages.

```css
/* ✅ Base prevention */
html, body {
  overflow-x: hidden;
  max-width: 100%;
}

/* ✅ Ensure all containers respect viewport width */
* {
  max-width: 100%;
}

img, video {
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}

/* ✅ Handle long text */
.text-content {
  word-wrap: break-word;
  overflow-wrap: break-word;
}

/* ❌ BAD - Fixed widths that exceed viewport */
.container {
  width: 1400px;
}

/* ✅ GOOD - Responsive widths */
.container {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 120rem; /* 1200px */
  padding: 0 2rem;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
```

