## Additional Best Practices

### Avoid Nesting in BEM
BEM is flat by design. Don't nest selectors.

```css
/* ❌ BAD */
.card {
  .card__title {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }
}

/* ✅ GOOD */
.card__title {
  font-size: 2rem;
}
```

### Use Consistent Spacing

```css
/* Use multiples of 0.4rem or 0.8rem for consistency */
.component {
  padding: 1.6rem; /* 16px */
  margin-bottom: 2.4rem; /* 24px */
  gap: 0.8rem; /* 8px */
}
```

### Responsive Design

```css
/* Mobile-first approach */
.card {
  padding: 1.6rem;
  font-size: 1.4rem;
}

/* Tablet and up */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .card {
    padding: 2.4rem;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }
}

/* Desktop and up */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .card {
    padding: 3.2rem;
  }
}
```
